$_SERVER :
It is the super global variable used to get the server configuration and server signature .
Like hostname,host agent, server variables ,query string ,methods,type of the request ,types of headers ,
etc. 

How to print multi dimensional Array ?
echo "<pre>";
print_r($_SERVER);
echo "</pre>";
exit;

Output:
